description: Notion OAuth patterns & ACs
alwaysApply: true
---

- Backend-owned Authorization Code flow; per-user token stored encrypted; proactive refresh.
- Endpoints: `/connect/notion`, `/oauth/notion/callback`; `notion_connections` table; Fernet encryption.
- Hosted Notion MCP (`mcp.notion.com/mcp`) per user; tool availability depends on connection status.
